  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You unleash a ripple of lightning forwards striking all those in front of your indiscriminately. All creatures in a 45-foot cone in front of you must succeed a Dexterity saving throw, taking 6d4 Lightning damage on a failed save or half as much on a successful one.</p><p><em><strong>Combination:</strong></em> <em>If this jutsu is cast as a Combination jutsu with 2 or more casters you increase the damage die by 3. Any creature who assists in casting this jutsu as a combination jutsu increases the damage of this jutsu by one step based on the highest Charisma Modifier within the group of casters. (+0-1: No Change, +2: D6, +3: D8, +4: D10, +5: D12).</em></p>",
